import React from 'react' import logo from '../images/Vector.svg' import Header from './Header.js' import Main from './Main.js' import Footer from './Footer.js' import PopupWithForm from './PopupWithForm.js' import ImagePopup from './ImagePopup.js' import '../../' function App() { const [isEditAvatarPopupOpen, setIsEditAvatarPopupOpen] = React.useState(false); const [isAddPlacePopupOpen, setIsAddPlacePopupOpen] = React.useState(false); const [isEditProfilePopupOpen, setIsEditProfilePopupOpen] = React.useState(false); const [selectedCard, setSelectedCard] = React.useState(false); function handleCardClick(card) { setSelectedCard(card); } function handleEditAvatarClick() { setIsEditAvatarPopupOpen(true); } function handleEditProfileClick() { setIsEditProfilePopupOpen(true); } function handleAddPlaceClick() { setIsAddPlacePopupOpen(true); } function closeAllPopups() { setIsEditAvatarPopupOpen(false); setIsEditProfilePopupOpen(false); setIsAddPlacePopupOpen(false); setSelectedCard(false); } return (
); } export default App;
